data.description: Another great listing offered by Stefanie Zimmerman, Re/Max Signature Properties, 785-579-5300.   This lovely townhome will meet your needs, as everything is conveniently offered on one level.  There are two spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms.   The open floor plan provides a good sized living room and spacious kitchen.   Side patio and fully fenced back yard add to the great features of this home.  One car attached garage.     Call Stefanie at 785-209-0816 for a private viewing.  https://www.hommati.com/3DTour-AerialVideo/unbranded/519-Brookmont-Dr-Manhattan-KS--HPI27580452
